title: Gentle Natural Wellness
sitename: Gentle Natural Wellness with Emily Ryan, ND, MSOM, LAc
cleaned_text: Meet Emily Ryan Imagine a doctor that takes the time to listen to your own personal story to help you achieve your optimal health through patient-focused care. As a Naturopathic Doctor and Acupuncturist, I can help you increase your energy and overall well-being through modalities such as classical homeopathy, acupuncture, and counseling to help you feel better.
